name: ext_R4B_MolecularSequence_quality
title: Cross-version Extension for R4B.MolecularSequence.quality for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version extension represents MolecularSequence.quality from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/MolecularSequence|4.3.0 for use in FHIR R5.

element.short: An set of value as quality of sequence
element.definition: An experimental feature attribute that defines the quality of the feature in a quantitative way, such as a phred quality score ([SO:0001686](http://www.sequenceontology.org/browser/current_svn/term/SO:0001686)).
